{
  "stem": "11744.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I mean there was always hope and with as long as you never got any official-- any official response-- I mean, to any other card that you send and any of the mail that you send through the Red Cross, they never got a response.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so, until that one card, that postcard came, I didn't know what happened to him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know whether he was prisoner or he had been killed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was all until he suddenly came in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I mean-- I remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can imagine what happened to-- to me and my children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, we-- we couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We couldn't-- we never believed what would happen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We never could tell.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the minute-- the minute he came back, I mean, the only thing he had in mind was to be in the resistance.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's all-- that's all that count for him, and he had to fight.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we could have come to America, because my parents in the meantime came to America in 1941, and we could have come.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But my husband always believed that being Jewish and-- and belonging to France, and being a French patriot, you don't flee to America.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was to fight for your country.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, then we settled.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We settled in another place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't stay where I was with the hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we settled in another place, and he almost immediately started to-- to work for the resistance.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think I told you a very interesting story that he was-- at that time he was managing a very big five and ten cents store.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When he got into the attic of that store, he found tons and tons of dry beans and sugar and green beans and yellow beans-- and tons of it.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
